{"tid":699514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［巴膠格鬥會］ 涉馬場施奪命鉸剪腳欺凌 24歲巴膠被捕","createTime":"2018-06-12T14:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T04:44:36.000Z","uid":72280,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"28869393522bc4eed1ab9fa04e263665423ec352","tid":699514,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:57:21.000Z","msg":"【欺凌巴士迷】14歲童馬場巴士站遭騎住打　雙膝跪地　警拘24歲男<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/225539_6b25089752ba8d02a3bd2879a1dbea45.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F225539_6b25089752ba8d02a3bd2879a1dbea45.png&h=d134bbf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/225515_70bb3ad3ebd2d1562f48817aadee1d2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F225515_70bb3ad3ebd2d1562f48817aadee1d2b.png&h=d3b42629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方在6月4日接獲舉報，指一名14歲男童，於6月3日下午，在沙田馬場一巴士內站被人襲擊。該名14歲男童當時頭部受傷，被送往明愛醫院治理。案件列作「襲擊致造成實際身體傷害」，由沙田警區刑事調查隊跟進。警方經調查後，昨日(12日)在機場警區拘捕一名24歲姓羅男子，涉嫌與案有關。被捕男子已獲准保釋候查，須於7月上旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，涉事兩人均為巴士迷，當日曾有兩人打架相片於網上流傳。一名紅衣男童雙腳跪地，另一名白衣男子騎在其背部，並以雙手分別按着其頸背及臉部。男童一度用手墊着額頭，臉部朝地。<br />\n<br />\n沙田馬場巴士站是巴士迷的「是非之地」，去年九月，一名巴士迷在同一地方，向拍攝巴士的青年作出挑釁，引發同場逾30多人爆發大罵戰，引起警方介入，成為巴士迷界的一時熱話。"},{"pid":"98969939b2f5e6b87d98cb07a3aa5b3b9f834262","tid":699514,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:11:11.000Z","msg":"24歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e578de02c1941b24efe33509ff7fc07c925b209f","tid":699514,"uid":55732,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:11:58.000Z","msg":"24歲都咁撚on9<br />\n<br />\n班巴膠個撚個都古靈精怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78e9b794aeae5017a4e5d9b5f513e91cc896291","tid":699514,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:16:48.000Z","msg":"巴膠真係好撚ON9，咪影衰港男啦"},{"pid":"d0b2abe4f67ad6177a943227583d116c5d4e515f","tid":699514,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"呢個站對巴膠黎講有咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e079c154812b0d0148a5e0eac9be42e2b1a84be","tid":699514,"uid":72280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:55:29.000Z","msg":"狗巴至今無回應"},{"pid":"6a74d4438a949e214bc69a721084e882ea5e85a1","tid":699514,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d93c21943e8b2fd42df4e489e8493bbf48d367a","tid":699514,"uid":103207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:59:57.000Z","msg":"打個自閉既細路仔，正一廢柴"},{"pid":"372aefa3e01c8c93dc466f31f3067b18414c95bc","tid":699514,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0b2abe4f67ad6177a943227583d116c5d4e515f","tid":699514,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"呢個站對巴膠黎講有咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:04:40.000Z","msg":"只係跑馬日開，啲車同路綫會有多人啲「特見」"},{"pid":"8e8c2bb258f03fca3454130e253f088e886b990d","tid":699514,"uid":12449,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"d0b2abe4f67ad6177a943227583d116c5d4e515f","tid":699514,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"呢個站對巴膠黎講有咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:05:55.000Z","msg":"宗教嘅聖地？好似麥加同耶路撒冷咁"},{"pid":"500cf2681b27018256bd759c1da25639d4d664c4","tid":699514,"uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite